{"tid":2256316,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英獲美學院頒信仰與自由獎","createTime":"2020-10-24T09:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T10:19:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"837babb0400c0e791e4fb891430fb70a434cd728","tid":2256316,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/X7OZ33MIWBCSZG56ZQEI5AZIDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FX7OZ33MIWBCSZG56ZQEI5AZIDI%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLDXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=164a68a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FX7OZ33MIWBCSZG56ZQEI5AZIDI%2F&h=8d528dac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/X7OZ33MIWBCSZG56ZQEI5AZIDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n黎智英獲美學院頒信仰與自由獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-3cMufugq-2-pjNHk0pN00CzMmI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/52TZ2DADGNEPXE4ZL6K2OLK5OE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-3cMufugq-2-pjNHk0pN00CzMmI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F52TZ2DADGNEPXE4ZL6K2OLK5OE.jpg&h=3ca50437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方早前搜查蘋果日報大樓，拘捕創辦人黎智英（圖）及相關高層，肆意打壓新聞自由。致力宣揚自由社會的美國阿克頓學院（Acton Institute）宣佈，將於下星期三（28日）網上向黎智英頒發「信仰與自由獎（The Faith and Freedom Award）」，以表揚黎智英在信仰及自由方面的努力。<br />\n<br />\n阿克頓學院於1990年成立，強調一個兼具自由與美德的社會，仰賴個人自由及宗教原則所維持。該學院不時會舉辦研討會及講座，亦會出版書籍、期刊及製作電影等宣揚自由理念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戴卓爾夫人曾獲殊榮<br />\n<br />\n阿克頓學院主席兼聯合創始人羅伯&middot;西里科牧師（Rev. Robert Sirico）在蘋果日報大樓被警方搜查當日發表聲明，批評警方以國安法作幌子搜查及拘捕，並讚揚黎智英是一個有堅定信念的人，有信心他不會被威嚇到，並指黎早已預計將發生的事情，亦已準備為自由付出代價。<br />\n<br />\n學院2000年成立「信仰與自由獎」，旨在表彰在公民、商業或宗教領域中有傑出表現的人士。.................................."},{"pid":"918c1ca1c2bd4658b745d9ffb372ba7d5b639d94","tid":2256316,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"星期三又搜蘋果總部啦"},{"pid":"5d06ed89d6df4e9167e37e5af00aeac036930fbb","tid":2256316,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:19:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}